symbols.name: async_complete
symbols.description: Async complete callback, triggered after the execution of any command that is executed asynchronously, for example various loading or saving related commands.

symbols.name: controller
symbols.description: MIDI controller callback, executed whenever a MIDI CC, Pitch Bend or Channel Pressure message is received.

symbols.name: init
symbols.description: Initialization callback, executed when the script was successfully compiled without warnings or errors.

symbols.name: listener
symbols.description: Listener callback, executed at definable time intervals or whenever a transport command is received.

symbols.name: note
symbols.description: Note callback, executed whenever a MIDI Note On message is received.

symbols.name: note_controller
symbols.description: MIDI 2.0 per-note controller callback, executed whenever a MIDI 2.0 Registered Per-Note Controller, MIDI 2.0 Assignable Per-Note Controller, or MIDI 2.0 Per-Note Pitch Bend message is received.

symbols.name: persistence_changed
symbols.description: Executed after the on init callback, or whenever a snapshot has been loaded.

symbols.name: pgs_changed
symbols.description: Executed whenever any pgs_set_key_val() command is executed in any script slot.

symbols.name: poly_at
symbols.description: Polyphonic aftertouch callback, executed whenever a MIDI Polyphonic Aftertouch message is received.

symbols.name: release
symbols.description: Release callback, executed whenever a MIDI Note Off message is received.

symbols.name: rpn
symbols.description: RPN callbacks, executed whenever a MIDI RPN (registered/non-registered parameter number) message is received.

symbols.name: nrpn
symbols.description: NRPN callbacks, executed whenever a MIDI NRPN (registered/non-registered parameter number) message is received.

symbols.name: ui_control
symbols.description: UI callback, executed whenever the user interacts with a particular UI widget.

symbols.name: ui_update
symbols.description: UI update callback, executed with every GUI change in Kontakt.

symbols.name: ui_controls
symbols.description: Global UI callback, executed whenever the user interacts with any particular UI widget.

symbols.name: midi_in
symbols.description: MIDI callback, triggered by every incoming MIDI event.
